        "content": "{{short description|English rugby league footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2020}}\n{{Use British English|date=February 2020}}\n{{Infobox rugby league biography\n|name                = Ray Handscombe\n|fullname            = Raymond Handscombe\n|image               =\n|imagesize           =\n|caption             =\n|birth_date          = first ¼ {{birth year and age|1950}}\n|birth_place         = Lower [[Agbrigg]] district, England\n|death_date          =\n|height              = \n|weight              = \n|position            = {{rlp|HK}}\n|club1               = [[Leeds Rhinos|Leeds]]\n|year1start          = ≤1974\n|year1end            = 74\n|appearances1        = \n|tries1              = \n|goals1              = \n|fieldgoals1         = \n|points1             = \n|club2               = [[Wakefield Trinity]]\n|year2start          = 1974\n|year2end            = 78\n|appearances2        = 132\n|tries2              = 16\n|goals2              = 0\n|fieldgoals2         = 2\n|points2             = 49\n|club3               = {{nowrap|[[Featherstone Rovers]]}}\n|year3start          = 1978\n|year3end            = 85\n|appearances3        = 126+1\n|tries3              = 15\n|goals3              = 0\n|fieldgoals3         = 0\n|points3             = 45\n|new                 = yes\n|retired             = yes\n|updated             = 7 July 2017\n|source              = <ref name=\"Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/players/raymond-handscombe/summary.html|title=Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org|publisher=rugbyleagueproject.org|date=31 December 2018|accessdate=1 January 2019}}</ref>\n}}\n\n'''Raymond \"Ray\" Handscombe''' (birth registered first ¼ 1950<ref name=\"Birth details at freebmd.org.uk\">{{cite web|url=http://www.freebmd.org.uk/cgi/information.pl?cite=zp1yb6P74cYn0LenSmBgDw&scan=1|title=Birth details at freebmd.org.uk|publisher=freebmd.org.uk|date=31 December 2016|accessdate=1 January 2017}}</ref>) is an English former professional [[rugby league]] footballer who played in the 1970s and 1980s. He played at club level for [[Leeds Rhinos|Leeds]], [[Wakefield Trinity]], and [[Featherstone Rovers]], as a {{rlp|hk}}.<ref name=\"Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org\"/>\n\n==Playing career==\nHandscombe made his début for [[Wakefield Trinity]] during September 1974, he played his last match for Wakefield Trinity during the [[1978–79 Northern Rugby Football League season|1978–79 season]], he made his début for [[Featherstone Rovers]] on Sunday 29 October 1978,<ref name=\"Bailey, Ron 20 September 2001\">Bailey, Ron (20 September 2001). ''Images of Sport - Featherstone Rovers Rugby League Football Club''. The History Press. {{ISBN|0752422952}}</ref> during his time at Featherstone Rovers he scored twenty-nine 3-point tries, and one 4-point try, and he played his last match for Featherstone Rovers during the [[1984–85 Rugby Football League season|1984–85 season]].\n\n===Challenge Cup Final appearances===\nHandscombe played {{rlp|hk}} in [[Featherstone Rovers]]' 14-12 victory over [[Hull F.C.]] in the [[1983 Challenge Cup]] Final during the [[1982–83 Rugby Football League season#Challenge Cup|1982–83 season]] at [[Wembley Stadium (1923)|Wembley Stadium]], [[London]] on Saturday 7 May 1983, in front of a crowd of 84,969.\n\n===County Cup Final appearances===\nHandscombe played {{rlp|hk}} in [[Wakefield Trinity]]'s 13-16 defeat by [[Hull Kingston Rovers]] in the [[1974 Yorkshire Cup]] Final during the [[1974–75 Northern Rugby Football League season|1974–75 season]] at [[Headingley Rugby Stadium|Headingley]], [[Leeds]] on Saturday 26 October 1974.{{citation needed|date=February 2020}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.rugbyleagueproject.org/players/Raymond-Handscombe/summary.html Statistics at rugbyleagueproject.org]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.com/2015/11/ray-handscombe.html Ray Handscombe]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.com/2012/ 2012]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2015/11/willis-fawley.html Willis Fawley]\n*[https://marklaspalmas.blogspot.com/2013/04/ April 2013]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.com/2011/08/number-seven-dream-chapter-thirteen.html Raymond Handscombe]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-i.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part I - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-ii.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part II - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-iii.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part III - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-iv.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part IV - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-v.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part V - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-vi.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part VI - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-vii.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part VII - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-viii.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part VIII - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-ix.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part IX - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[http://marklaspalmas.blogspot.co.uk/2013/04/the-story-of-wembley-1983-part-x.html The Story of Wembley 1983. Part X - a featherstone rovers blog]\n*[https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/search/results?basicsearch=%22Raymond%20Handscombe%22&retrievecountrycounts=false Search for \"Raymond Handscombe\" at britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk]\n*[https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/search/results?basicsearch=%22Ray%20Handscombe%22&retrievecountrycounts=false Search for \"Ray Handscombe\" at britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk]\n\n{{Featherstone Rovers - 1983 Challenge Cup Final winners}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Handscombe, Raymond}}\n[[Category:1950 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:English rugby league players]]\n[[Category:Featherstone Rovers players]]\n[[Category:Leeds Rhinos players]]\n[[Category:Rugby league hookers]]\n[[Category:Rugby league players from Wakefield]]\n[[Category:Wakefield Trinity players]]"
