        "title": "Heoclisis",
        "content": "{{Short description|Genus of insects}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=December 2021}}\n{{Automatic taxobox\n| image = Heoclisis fundata.jpg\n| image_caption = ''[[Heoclisis fundata]]''\n| taxon = Heoclisis\n| authority = [[Longinos Navás|Navás]], 1923\n}}\n\n'''''Heoclisis''''' is a genus of cave-dwelling<ref name=\"miller\" /> [[antlion]]s, that is, insects in the family [[Myrmeleontidae]].<ref name=\"afd\">{{Cite web|url=https://biodiversity.org.au/afd/taxa/Heoclisis|title=Australian Faunal Directory: ''Heoclisis'' Navás, 1923\n|access-date=2021-12-28|website=biodiversity.org.au}}</ref>\n\nThe genus was first described by [[Longinos Navás]] in 1923.<ref name=\"afd\" /><ref name=\"navas\">{{cite journal|author=Navás, L.|authorlink=Longinos Navás |date= 1923|title= Insecta nova, Ser. 8–10|journal= Memorie dell'Accademia Pontificia dei Nuovi Lincei |volume= 2\n|issue=6|pages= 1-27 [12]}}</ref>\n\nMiller and Stange (2012)<ref name=miller>{{cite Q|Q110156772}}</ref> describe them as not being true cave-dwelling antlions, because  not all life stages are confined to caves.\n\n==Species==\nThese species belong to the genus ''Heoclisis'':<ref name=\"itis\">{{cite web|title=ITIS: ''Heoclisis'' Report|url=https://www.itis.gov/servlet/SingleRpt/SingleRpt?search_topic=TSN&search_value=981472#null|website=Integrated Taxonomic Information System|accessdate=2021-12-28}}</ref><ref name=\"afd\" />\n*''[[Heoclisis acuta]]'' <small>(Kimmins, 1939)</small>\n*''[[Heoclisis angustipennis]]'' <small>New, 1985</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis conspurcata]]'' <small>(Gerstaecker, 1885)</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis fulva]]'' <small>(Esben-Petersen, 1912)</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis fulvifusa]]'' <small>(Kimmins, 1939)</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis fundata]]'' <small>(Walker, 1853)</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis japonica]]'' <small>(Hagen, 1866)</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis louiseae]]'' <small>Banks, 1938</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis ramosa]]'' <small>New, 1985</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis sinensis]]'' <small>Navás, 1923</small>\t \n*''[[Heoclisis tillyardi]]'' <small>(Kimmins, 1939)</small>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n}}\n==External links==\n*[https://www.gbif.org/species/2099131 ''Heoclisis'': images & occurrence data] from [[GBIF]]\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q10522178}}\n\n[[Category:Myrmeleontidae]]\n[[Category:Taxa named by Longinos Navás]]\n[[Category:Taxa described in 1923]]\n\n\n{{antlion-stub}}"
