        "title": "Bak Yeong-hee",
        "content": "{{Short description|South Korean voice actress}}\n{{family name hatnote|[[Park (Korean surname)|Bak]]||lang=Korean}}\n'''Bak Yeong-hee''' ({{Korean|hangul=박영희}}; born November 27, 1959, in [[Busan]]) is a South Korean [[Voice acting|voice actress]] who joined the [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation]]'s [[MBC Voice Acting Division|Voice Acting Division]] in 1982, which is fan club headquartered in [[Goyang]], [[Gyeonggi-do]], South Korea.\n\n==Roles==\n===Broadcast TV===\n* [[Ojamajo Doremi]] (Magical Remi from 1st - 3rd Series, Korea TV Edition, MBC and TV Special of Korea Edition, Tooniverse)\n* [[Mirmo!]] ([[Mirmo Pong Pong Pong]], Korea TV Edition, SBS)\n* [[CSI: Miami]] (replacing [[Sofia Milos]] by season 2–3, Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* [[Buffy the Vampire Slayer]] (replacing [[Charisma Carpenter]], Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* [[MacGyver (1985 TV series)|MacGyver]] (Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* Miracle Girls (Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* Time Adventure (Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* Knight Boy Ramu (Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* Adventure King's Gulliver (Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* Robinhood Adventure (Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* Escaplowne (Korea TV Edition, SBS)\n* Minky (Korea TV Edition, SBS)\n* [[El Hazard]] (Korea TV Edition, Tooniverse)\n* Chun Chie in Love (Korea TV Edition, Tooniverse)\n* Lupang (Korea TV Edition, Tooniverse)\n\n=== Movie Dubbing ===\n* [[Star Wars]] (replacing [[Carrie Fisher]], Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* [[Autumn in New York (film)|Autumn in New York]] (replacing [[Winona Ryder]], Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* [[The Butterfly Effect]] (replacing [[Melora Walters]], Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* [[Elf (film)|Elf]] (replacing [[Mary Steenburgen]], Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n* [[Chicago (2002 film)|Chicago]] (replacing [[Renée Zellweger]], Korea TV Edition, MBC)\n\n==See also==\n* [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation]]\n* [[MBC Voice Acting Division]]\n\n==External links==\n* [http://voicepyh.fanpy.com Yeong Hee Cham Sa Rang Fan Club Homepage] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051030145541/http://voicepyh.fanpy.com/ |date=2005-10-30 }} (in Korean)\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110604010525/http://www.mbcvoice.net/profile/profile_main.php?pageMode=viewProfile&pMode=&uid=81&now_page=5&sortMode=0&searchCategory=&searchWord= MBC Voice Acting division Bak Yeong Hee blog] (in Korean)\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bak, Yeong Hee}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:South Korean voice actresses]]\n[[Category:1959 births]]\n[[Category:People from Busan]]\n\n\n{{SouthKorea-voice-actor-stub}}"
